<strong>Primary Care</strong>
<ul class="single"><li>
 Does the patient have a primary care provider? If not, provide referral.
</li></ul><br />


<strong>Partner Information</strong>
<ul class="single"><li>
 Determine whether partners are known to be HIV-infected
</li></ul>
<br />
<em>For patients with an HIV-infected partner, ask:</em>
<ul class="single"><li>
 <em>Is partner(s) receiving ART?</em></li>
 <li><em>Is a resistance profile available?</em>
</li></ul>
